@@citzAnd place my own soul in my palm?
<p></p>
</br>15 Even if he would slay me, would I not wait?
@@citzI would only argue to his face for my own ways.
<p></p>
</br>16 He would also be my salvation,
@@citzFor before him no apostate will come in.
<p></p>
