@@citzAnd regard me as an enemy of yours?
<p></p>
</br>25 Will you make a mere leaf driven about quiver,
@@citzOr keep chasing after mere dry stubble?
<p></p>
</br>26 For you keep writing against me bitter things
@@citzAnd you make me possess [the consequences of] the errors of my youth.
<p></p>
