@@citzEven the very number of years that have been reserved for the tyrant.
<p></p>
</br>21 The sound of dreadful things is in his ears;
@@citzDuring peace a despoiler himself comes upon him.
<p></p>
</br>22 He does not believe that he will come back out of darkness,
@@citzAnd he is reserved for a sword.
<p></p>
