</br>2 “Can an able-bodied man be of use to God himself,
@@citzThat anyone having insight should be of use toward him?
<p></p>
</br>3 Does the Almighty have any delight in that you are righteous,
@@citzOr any gain in that you make your way blameless?
<p></p>
</br>4 For your reverence will he reprove you,
@@citzWill he come with you into the judgment?
<p></p>
