@@citzAlso see the sum total of the stars, that they are high.
<p></p>
</br>13 And yet you have said: ‘What does God really know?
@@citzThrough thick gloom can he judge?
<p></p>
</br>14 Clouds are a concealment place for him so that he does not see,
@@citzAnd on the vault of heaven he walks about.’
<p></p>
