@@citzAnd the quarreling of his bones is continual.
<p></p>
</br>20 And his life certainly makes bread loathsome,
@@citzAnd his own soul desirable food.
<p></p>
</br>21 His flesh wastes away from sight,
@@citzAnd his bones that were not seen certainly grow bare.
<p></p>
</br>22 And his soul draws near to the pit,
@@citzAnd his life to those inflicting death.
